article.headline: Smith's 17 lead Alabama A&M past Mississippi Valley State 78-70
article.linkText: Smith's 17 lead Alabama A&M past Mississippi Valley State 78-70
article.story: ITTA BENA, Miss. -- — Dailin Smith's 17 points helped Alabama A&M defeat Mississippi Valley State 78-70 on Monday night. Smith also added seven rebounds for the Bulldogs (3-12, 2-0 Southwestern Athletic Conference). Lorenzo Downey scored 14 points and added five rebounds. EJ Williams was 6 of 13 shooting and 1 of 4 from the free throw line to finish with 13 points. Rayquan Brown and Donovan Sanders each scored 23 points for the Delta Devils (0-15, 0-2). Darrius Clark finished with seven points and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
